gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 123, Jazz 116
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Jazz, 123-116. Klay Thompson led Golden State with 25 points, three rebounds, and three assists as Andrew Wiggins added 19 points. Keyonte George led the Jazz with 21 points. Golden State finishes the season at 46-36 as the Jazz end at 31-51.
